<HL>
   Some Big U.S. Companies Favor
   Loosening Anti-Dumping Laws
   ----
   By Eduardo Lachica
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/31/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
</SO>
<CO>
   JAPAN CANDA EUROP IBM HWP CAT
</CO>
